    "attributes": {
      "name": "Table Seating Planner",
      "summary": "Seating charts are the most stressful part of planning an event — dozens of guests, family politics, and a floor plan that keeps changing right up to the big day. Table Seating Planner takes the pain out of it: lay out your venue with drag-and-drop tables and fixtures (or import your own floor plan), then seat everyone with a simple drag.\n\nOpen the demo to see it shine: ask the AI assistant to arrange the seats and watch every guest find a place, step through the guided setup wizard to start an event of your own, then carry your theme through to matching invitations and posters for the big day.",
